song_name: Nevermind The Cowboysherees The Real Russains

version_description: There was no chords for this beautiful song on this app/website, so I decided to add them. I don't say they are perfectly correct but very close, I think. Hope you like it.
You can play power chords in chorus.
Original tuning half step down. Or you can transpose 5 steps down and put capo on 4th fret, so that can be played along with easy chords (G)..
They play that acoustically in that key. You can put capo on 2nd fret if playing along the record. Add11-chords can simplify if needed.
Acoustic campfire version, you can play with standard tuning.
